          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ventilator</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Siemens Elema, Uppsala</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Sweden</ENAMEX>) using the
